{
  "text": "To integrate previously developed physical map [CITATION_1] with the highdensity linkage map constructed in the present work, all the mapped SNPs with 70-bp flanking sequences were aligned with BES [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] and BAC-based physical map contig-specific sequences (PMCSS) [CITATION_4] using",
  "correct_citation": {
